name: Swing of Lass
description:
Daughters are a blessing for parents."Sing of Lass" is transformation of the girl child to the girl to woman to grandmother. This artwork show relation of a girl with the world with different roles and responsibility like daughter, sister, friend, wife, mother, grandmother, and many more. How the life of a girl evolves in every time period and phase of life makes them stronger and gives strength to give new life to the world. in this artwork, you see the daughter is swinging in the hands of her parents which represents the care she gets from her parents. swinging show the joy of childhood. she has a heart-shaped balloon in hand which shows how she spread love in the world.
The colors in this artwork are vibrant to show the nature, diversification, and strength of the girl. how parents grow old in growing up a child shown in the hand sculpture shown in the artwork.
